{"tid":1683904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武警深圳灣集結演練　水炮車出動射水","createTime":"2019-10-31T00:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T00:27:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68068c7b36f8e880fae74984a6edececc5a7a31b","tid":1683904,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_01b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=845bf1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該批身穿防暴裝備的武警，在演習現場與持械人士展開訓練。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_02b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=dc4558cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有水炮車在現場噴水。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_03b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=5d603dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有武警模擬為同袍包紮。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_04b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=6c780a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n演習現場出動一批水炮車和裝甲車。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_05b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=ed5d6fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有武警為模擬頭部受傷的同袍包紮傷口。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_06b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=b543c692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有武警手持棍狀武器和盾牌的裝備，與戴上頭盔的同袍展開搏鬥訓練。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_07b.jpg?20191030215932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20191030215932&h=3466a3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場位於深圳灣體育中心附近。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<br />\n香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》風波未息，武警部隊繼續集結在廣東深圳市深圳灣的春繭體育館內。美聯社周三（30日）發布新一批照片，全副裝備的武警在場館外展開防暴演習，亦有武警模擬為頭部受傷的同袍包紮，同場有水炮車射水。<br />\n<br />\n從照片可見，身穿迷彩服、佩備盾牌及警棍的武警在足球場，與手持長武器、戴頭盔的同袍展開攻防演練。另有一批武警為模擬頭部受傷的同袍包紮傷口，附近放滿盾牌及頭盔等裝備。現場附近泊滿多輛軍車、裝甲車，一輛水炮車駛過及射水。<br />\n<br />\n法新社早前報道指，數千名武警於本年8月中進駐春繭體育館，在場內列隊演練，場外集結多輛軍車及裝甲車。有美國有線新聞網絡記者稱，曾在場館內採訪，遭武警軍官驅趕離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=8ffb16cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"978a4d55a72e0cc4e78bb202be4461c712abb752","tid":1683904,"uid":149607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"Train好就入黎扮差佬"}]}